100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-6.htm">中國南方白話字發展</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-7.htm">台灣基督教長老教會簡表</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-8.htm">台灣基督教長老教會教會歷史委員會</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-9.htm">《北部台灣基督長老教會教會ê歷史》</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-10.htm">關於陳清忠</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-12.htm">白話字文學：台灣文學的早春</a></td></tr></table>
